==========
LpOD 0.9.3
==========

lpOD -- languages & platforms OpenDocument.
Definition of a Free Software API implementing the ISO/IEC 26300 standard.
Development, for higher level use cases, in Python, Perl and Ruby languages.
of a top-down oriented API.

This release is mostly a clean-up release with method names shortened.

The table API simplification was delayed to 0.9.4 which will hopefully take
less time to release. Integration of charts and OpenFormula is also planned.

- Web: http://lpod-project.net
- Documentation: http://docs.lpod-project.net
- IRC: irc://irc.freenode.org/lpod

Low-level API
=============

The name shortenings are numerous so we group them by module.

The basic idea is:

    Before                         After
    -----------------------------  ----------------------
    get_cell_xxx                   get_xxx
    get_row_xxx                    get_xxx
    get_column_xxx                 get_xxx
    get_table_xxx                  get_xxx
    is_table_xxx                   get_xxx
    get_page_xxx                   get_xxx
    get_frame_xxx                  get_xxx
    get_note_xxx                   get_xxx
    get_annotation_xxx             get_xxx
    get_style_xxx                  get_xxx
    get_toc_xxx                    get_xxx

But some remain (e.g., get_xxx_list).

